    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735570/extras/24fa9490a088c18e58c01627908b4e62.webp?t=1667212634\" width=620 height=60 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The story</h2><br>London, 1871, we are in the middle of the <strong>Steampunk</strong> era of the Victorian era.<br>A mad genius wants to destroy the city from underground to show his power and impose his will on the whole of England.<br><br>To carry out his evil plan, he has scattered explosive charges  throughout underground London, in strategic places, to be detonated soon.<br>Fortunately, we were able to find a few that our agents were able to defuse.<br><br><strong>You Are Our Last Chance!</strong><br>With your <strong>revolutionary turbine ship</strong>, you will descend into the depths of the city to retrieve our agents, as well as the explosive charges they have stored in containers.<br>Good luck!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735570/extras/0eafea11296fed54cbbc2c2d300a2844.webp?t=1667212634\" width=620 height=60 /></span><br><br>Your ship is a flying submarine, powered by powerful revolutionary turbines, allowing you to propel yourself both in the air and in the water.<br>You'll need practice to handle it with dexterity!<br><br>You will have to recovery men and put them on the platforms that you will use to repair your ship.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735570/extras/af2bb91ef9242fdeeca183fdfcaf9689.poster.avif?t=1667212634\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735570/extras/af2bb91ef9242fdeeca183fdfcaf9689.webm?t=1667212634\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735570/extras/af2bb91ef9242fdeeca183fdfcaf9689.mp4?t=1667212634\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You will also need to recovery heavy containers containing explosive charges and place them on the platforms.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735570/extras/ede705e809a3271e6f75231681c6eead.poster.avif?t=1667212634\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735570/extras/ede705e809a3271e6f75231681c6eead.webm?t=1667212634\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735570/extras/ede705e809a3271e6f75231681c6eead.mp4?t=1667212634\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Your ship can navigate underwater, but beware of the many devastating obstacles!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735570/extras/884914ac1908c901ba02a2906e8bb440.poster.avif?t=1667212634\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735570/extras/884914ac1908c901ba02a2906e8bb440.webm?t=1667212634\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735570/extras/884914ac1908c901ba02a2906e8bb440.mp4?t=1667212634\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Evaluations / Awards</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735570/extras/0685edf816a5e3ac44dbc16ef7b61d83.avif?t=1667212634\" width=314 height=176 /></span>",
